@2301   = ~ARCHER: The Archer is the epitome of skill with the bow, able to make almost any shot, no matter how difficult. To become so skilled with the bow, the Archer has had to sacrifice some proficiency with melee weapons and armor.

Advantages:
- +1 to hit and damage rolls with ranged weapon at levels 3, 6, 10, 15, and 21.
