@5211   = ~Secrets of the Spellfilchers~
@5212   = ~SPELLFILCHER: The Spellfilchers are hidden society of very specialized thieves.  They hone their abilities toward a dangerous goal: stealing magic from wizards. Spellfilchers have developed a few special tricks they can employ when confronted by angry mages.

Abilities:
- Once per day, Spellfilchers may cast the priest spell "Silence 15' Radius" 
- At 5th level Spellfilchers can cast a special variant of "Spell Turning" which only turns back a single spell, but lasts for 12 hours.
